00:24:26.150 --> 00:24:28.550
I'll go back and correct
those, because then there

00:24:28.550 --> 00:24:35.240
should have been an over A.
There should have been an over

00:24:35.240 --> 00:24:38.300
A. There should
have been an over A.

00:24:38.300 --> 00:24:40.710
Thank you for pointing that out.

00:24:40.710 --> 00:24:43.100
And there should
have been another--

00:24:43.100 --> 00:24:47.190
oh, in this case we can
just cancel all of the A's.

00:24:47.190 --> 00:24:48.750
I knew it came out
